SELECT
  `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_customer_id` AS `d_customer_id`,
  `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_customer_first_name` AS `d_customer_first_name`,
  `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_customer_last_name` AS `d_customer_last_name`,
  `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_customer_login` AS `d_customer_login`,
  `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_birth_country` AS `d_birth_country`,
  `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_customer_email_address` AS `d_customer_email_address`
FROM
  `tpc-ds benchmark model`.`tpc-ds benchmark model` `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`
WHERE
  (
    `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`Catalog Preferred`
    AND (
      `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`Sold Calendar Year-Week` = 2001
    )
    AND (
      `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_c_preferred_cust_flag` = 'Y'
    )
  )
GROUP BY
  1,
  2,
  3,
  4,
  5,
  6
ORDER BY
  1,
  2,
  3,
  4
LIMIT 100
